NAME
  VTK::ImagingHybridIO
LIBRARY_NAME
  vtkImagingHybridIO
DESCRIPTION
  vtkSliceCubes split out of ImagingHybrid: it isosurfaces volume slices read
  through a vtkVolumeReader (VTK::IOImage). Kept in its own module so that
  VTK::ImagingHybrid stays free of any IO dependency.
GROUPS
  Imaging
  StandAlone
SPDX_LICENSE_IDENTIFIER
  BSD-3-Clause
SPDX_COPYRIGHT_TEXT
